name: no. 013 - WOODSTOCK *SPECIAL*
description:
This is a bonus card for collectors who collect a complete set of OCTOBER 2021 series (12 cards).It's only being minted for a number of complete sets that can be collected after all the unsold of the series has been burned.

ON DEATH, LIFE AND WHATNOTS trading card is a collectible series made by Feransis using his artworks and things he learned from the internet. The subjects on these cards are stuff that he often thinks  about in everyday life.

For this OCTOBER 2021 series, he picks 12 subjects that can feel scary, evil, disgusting and monstrous.

OCTOBER 2021 series contains 9 regular type cards, 2 rare type cards, and 1 ultra rare type card. PLUS 1 special type card.
